Paper: hep-th/0207013

Date: 2002-07-01

Title: Cancellation of Global Anomalies in Spontaneously Broken Gauge Theories

Authors: M. Fabbrichesi, R. Percacci, M. Piai and M. Serone

Comments: 5 pages; v2

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D66 (2002) 105028

We discuss the generalization to global gauge anomalies of the familiarprocedure for the cancellation of local gauge anomalies in effective theoriesof spontaneously broken symmetries. We illustrate this mechanism in a recentlyproposed six-dimensional extension of the standard model.